{
  "stem": "523.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When my-- when my eyes got used to the darkness, it was a mountain of corpses, dead Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Young, old, children, naked, undressed were lying one on top of the other one.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At last, we were sitting down in the mud and in the dirt.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I saw a young girl was holding something covered.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't know what it is.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She said, this is her dead mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She didn't want to throw it up there with the dead people, so she was sleeping, living to-- near her dead mother.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Did--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They weren't allowed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would just insist they have to lie there in the-- nobody-- The Romanian did not allow to take people to-- to bury those people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Never mind a decent burial-- bury in a mass grave, but don't let them rot in such a condition.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So and the-- and the people around on the floor were mostly half dead already, because in such a condition, it was winter, cold.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the next day, the people were still half a life were forced to march to another place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was near Bershad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And Bershad was a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we passed by Bershad to another barn.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There-- there they were a place where pigs were kept before the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If was cold in winter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my parents realized that here in this barn, we would froze-- freeze to death.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because from there, this was supposed to be there not to go nowhere.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We knew that this is to die.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my parents thought we would go to Bershad.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was not allowed to get out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they risked their lives.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We will die in this barn.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We will die no matter what.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we walked about three or five kilometers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
